\int\limits _{0}^{w}\frac{dt}{\sqrt{(t^{2}+a^{2})(t^{2}+b^{2})}}=\frac{1}{a}\eF{\varphi}{k},\qquad\qquad w=b\tan\varphi\label{eq:ellf_ab}\end{equation}

