\layout Proof


\begin_inset Formula \[
\frac{M\msp d\theta}{\sqrt{1-\lambda^{2}\sin^{2}\theta}}=\frac{d\varphi}{\sqrt{1-k^{2}\sin^{2}\varphi}}\]

